  "title": "Luxury Retail Advisors | $2500-$4000 | Commissions | Central Region",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Advisors (Luxury brands) X 20 @ Central/East | Fast Hiring | $$$</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong>Central/East Region</p><p>💼 <strong>Job Type:</strong>Full-Time</p><p>🕒 <strong>Timing/Shifts:</strong>Retail Hours, Roster-Based / 44 hours work week</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Are you passionate about luxury fashion, personalized styling, and creating unforgettable client experiences?</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>✨ <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver a world-class luxury shopping experience to every client.</li><li>Provide expert styling advice and personalized product recommendations.</li><li>Build and nurture long-term client relationships through clienteling and follow-ups.</li><li>Consistently achieve or exceed individual and boutique sales targets.</li><li>Uphold brand image and luxury service standards at all times.</li><li>Support visual merchandising, stock management, and store events.</li></ul><p>🌟 <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Experience in <strong>luxury or premium fashion retail</strong> preferred.</li><li>Sales-driven, confident, and proactive in achieving targets.</li><li>Impeccable grooming and professionalism.</li></ul><p></p><p>📩 <strong>Apply Now</strong></p><p>Send your resume (MS Word format) to:</p><p>📱 WhatsApp / Telegram: 8509 0409</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period and expected salary in your application.</p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p><p>—</p><p>Annie Hoang (R25158747)</p><p>CREW by HRnet |HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd </p><p>EA24C2435</p>",
